{"tid":1834261,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"工作地方唔比人戴口罩（純發洩）","createTime":"2020-01-22T10:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T04:16:13.000Z","uid":235553,"like":59,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d3b39e9095595bf1a430a3eee7e033373ddc5a","tid":1834261,"uid":235553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"好向左走向右走嬲<br />\n我番工嘅地方係學校黎<br />\n但最高領導唔鐘意人戴口罩<br />\n所以唔比人戴口罩，小朋友戴口罩比佢見到<br />\n佢會「溫柔地」叫個小朋友除口罩<br />\n<br />\n但到左今日，香港都有確診武漢肺炎病例<br />\n都依然唔比工作時間戴口罩<br />\n革命是要流血的<br />\n射波射到重光先番工<br />\n要炒就炒啦，生命誠可貴<br />\n<br />\n響咁嘅工作環境下番工<br />\n感覺唔安全不極之不適<br />\n<br />\n希望小朋友放假唔好入中國啦<br />\n番學唔好帶菌令學校變疫區<br />\n<br />\n小朋友是無辜的<br />\n我都是無辜的<br />\n#黑警無一個是無辜的 #黑警死全家"},{"pid":"7733cc49b876ccf7f27520d87b8be2c1ce7082b7","tid":1834261,"uid":143151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"要等啲家長知<br />\n家長最care 衛生<br />\n未諗到好計 推下先"},{"pid":"68344aa10313a13ad6b34e0f530a8423c2f6c2bc","tid":1834261,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"咳比佢睇啦"},{"pid":"f8d648bf1a666c16820cda6f5668d92ffb37b98a","tid":1834261,"uid":99356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c7157858b7033412d998a1a136ba8a6d2a0dc45","tid":1834261,"uid":104758,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1837c6916879a592c432b5e8d2b8c1d68da04ddf","tid":1834261,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"細路仔唔會識咩事<br />\n一係開名推，一係令小朋友返屋企話畀父母知"},{"pid":"0b94e16c8b80c0f54b00da4ec2ec9a3d2fe2ac40","tid":1834261,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"使撚理九佢咩 最多咪記缺點<br />\n根本無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac